Package com.IGallinari.LastGame.service.API_to_DB.HandleJSON

Interface Handler

All Known Implementing Classes:
GamesHandler, GamesStatisticsHandler, PlayersHandler, PlayersStatisticsHandler, StandingsHandler, TeamsHandler, TeamsStatisticsHandler
public interface Handler
Interface for handling JSON nodes. Provides the functionality to process JSON data and convert it into various data types.
